[\autoref{prop:construction-intro}]\label{cor:construction}
 For nonnegative integers~$n$, $k$, $b$, $r$, $s$ with $n,k,b \geq 1$ and $r \leq b$, and with~$p$ and~$q$ as given in \autoref{def:pqdef}, we have

        $\alphag(E_{p/q}^{\boxtimes n}) \geq p.$
